  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Your Personal Ds Assistant\n\nDiscover how to use your Nintendo DS in a whole new way with the adorable Hello Kitty!\n\nJoin the iconic feline as you track your daily activities, update your friend directory, write in your diary and more.\n\nLet Hello Kitty Daily manage your busy life and stay organized in style!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
